sentences: Dalfidan was born in 1975 to Turkish parents and raised in the German industrial town of Solingen.
After a brief career as a music therapist, she attended Amsterdam Conservatory in 2006.
In 2008 she performed a series of concerts with the Tineke Postma Group, extending into the first half of 2009.
